         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Thaisous to Syras her mother. Know that Seleukos came here and has fled. Do not trouble yourself to embark. Wait till the anniversary. Lucia, write to me the day. Greet Ammonas my brother and -rapis and my sister ... and my father Theonas.


</ab>
